  "original_title": "\u0b86\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0b9f\u0bc8 - \u0b95\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc7\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0b9f\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Interim injunction against transfer of teachers - Kalmunai High Court Action",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Kalmunai High Court has issued an interim injunction against the transfer of 07 teachers on duty in the Kalmunai Education Zone by the Eastern Provincial Ministry of Education to other zones.",
        "The Writ of Certiorari under the provisions of Article 154 P (4) (b) of the Constitution was summoned in the presence of Kalmunai High Court Judge Hon. Troxy last (24).",
        "In this case, the Provincial Director of Education of the Eastern Provincial Department of Education, Mrs. Nakuleswari Pillainayakam, Additional Provincial Director of Education J. Arulanantham and the Secretary to the Ministry of Education, Eastern Province were named as defendants.",
        "After hearing the arguments of the petitioners, the Hon'ble High Court Judge directed that the case be re-called on Monday (27).",
        "When the petition was called for support again on Monday (27), the lawyers appearing on behalf of the petitioners submitted lengthy submissions that it was unreasonable and lawful to grant the petitioners an unauthorized transfer under Section 185 of the Establishment Procedure Code of the Eastern Provincial Public Service.",
        "Satisfied with the submissions, the High Court Judge issued an interim injunction restraining the transfer of the petitioners and directed them to send notice to the respondents appearing before the Hon'ble House (01).",
        "Attorney MM on behalf of the petitioners in the case. Senior lawyer Arif Samsuddin, lawyer Khalid Muhaimin and lawyer Mubarak Assam appeared on Nur Jahan's instructions."
      ],
